  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd -\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The main opposition alleges that the government plan to privatize fuel supply by deliberately creating fuel shortages",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The plan of the government is to create a planned fuel shortage in the country, make people wait in queues for a long time, and make the people say through their mouths that they will hand over the fuel supply to any private company.",
        "United People's Shakti Member of Parliament Ashoka Abeysinghe has accused that the government is trying to privatize the country's important resources.",
        "He said the above while participating in a press conference organized at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo (1) on Friday. There he added:",
        "Due to the actions of the government, the country is currently facing massive crises and is falling into the abyss.",
        "The food security level of our country has been completely destroyed and people have to wait in long queues to get essential commodities.",
        "The current Ranil-Rajapaksa government is meeting the representatives of those countries and publishing the photo saying that they have requested help from the international countries to solve the economic crisis.",
        "Through that they have built a political system of photography. But still there is no improvement in the economic situation.",
        "Sagala Ratnayake says that the next fuel ship will arrive in the country after the 22nd. So till then people will have to face massive crisis without fuel.",
        "He said that the plan of the government is to create a planned fuel shortage, make people wait in queues for a long time and make them say through their mouths that they should hand over the fuel supply to any private company."
      ],
